= Installation Instructions =
  * Install required modules - DataObjectManager and Uploadify.
  * Run dev/build
  * Install podcast module
  * Run dev/build

A new page type will appear in the CMS "Podcast Page". 
  * Create one of these and configure the details for the podcast on the "Podcast Details" tab. 
  * Upload your first episode on the "Episodes" tab.

Done.

More comprehensive instructions coming soon...